{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">You're just a simple farmer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some animals generate gold, others collect gold, and yet more can defend your herd. Every creature has a place on your farm.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">With two double-barreled shotguns</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When the forest comes a knockin' let your guns do the talking. With the help of your dogs, put a stop to the wild beasts that emerge from the trees. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Who just wants to have the most impressive flock the world has ever seen</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the size of your herd increases, so does their power. You can upgrade your existing creatures to make them more powerful or you can swap your animals with new ones you've discovered. Variety is key to ensure you are prepared for the dangers ahead.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Speaking of discovering new animals</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Destroy enemies to discover new herd mates. Certain enemies carry a box on their back; if you can dispatch them, a new animal will be added to your stable of available buddies.\u00a0</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980150/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736235588","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980150/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736235588","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980150/d8dd53db91c0720c7012917c88189d21dd699174/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736235588","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980150/d8dd53db91c0720c7012917c88189d21dd699174/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736235588","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">You're just a simple farmer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some animals generate gold, others collect gold, and yet more can defend your herd. Every creature has a place on your farm.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">With two double-barreled shotguns</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When the forest comes a knockin' let your guns do the talking. With the help of your dogs, put a stop to the wild beasts that emerge from the trees. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Who just wants to have the most impressive flock the world has ever seen</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the size of your herd increases, so does their power. You can upgrade your existing creatures to make them more powerful or you can swap your animals with new ones you've discovered. Variety is key to ensure you are prepared for the dangers ahead.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Speaking of discovering new animals</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Destroy enemies to discover new herd mates. Certain enemies carry a box on their back; if you can dispatch them, a new animal will be added to your stable of available buddies.\u00a0</p>","developers":["Polygon Dust Entertainment Ltd."],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980150/header.jpg?t=1736235588","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257079463,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257079463/movie480.mp4?t=1733812771","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257079463/movie_max.mp4?t=1733812771"},"name":"Prerelease Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257079463/6dd2db5dd8d5db42a1b31d2d2812bea12b86feb2/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1733812771","webm":{"480":